{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">GAMEPLAY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A physics-based platformer about a drone looking for a way. You are hovering above the ground with electric beams. Your goal is to angle the thrusters to overcome increasingly difficult obstacles. The controls are difficult, but mastering them is all the more satisfying! It is the definition of<strong> \u201ceasy to start, hard to master\u201d.</strong><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252730/extras/HoverGrooveGif1.gif?t=1729703616\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you hit an obstacle a little too hard, you will restart from the last checkpoint. It might be frustrating, but then you can just pause - relax and listen to this amazing soundtrack. When you settle down, try again - and again.<strong><i> </i></strong><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252730/extras/HoverGrooveGif2.gif?t=1729703616\" /><strong><i> </i></strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">CONTROLS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You use your mouse to control the drone. When the red dot is moving closer to the right side of the pad, right thrusters are being activated, and so on and so forth.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252730/extras/HoverGrooveGif3-3.gif?t=1729703616\" />If you place the red dot in the middle of the pad, the drone will hover peacefully in place. And that\u2019s it. I hope you will enjoy this little adventure ;)</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"First Checkpoint","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3252730/fa02455c7f1d205592b779304a6dcf5910f969a8.jpg"},{"name":"Second Achievement","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3252730/b098d133c40c4a916b4ec081ee4695a52c17dcb3.jpg"},{"name":"Third Checkpoint","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamst